headline.print_headline: Browns Dominate Bengals 24-3, Move Into 1st Place
headline.main: Browns Dominate Bengals 24-3, Move Into 1st Place

lead_paragraph: Cornerback Joe Haden led a line of Browns players jumping to slap hands with joyous fans in the first row. The stadium was filled with the sound of woofing.
